@page "/remote"
@using PureWave.Web.Data

<PageTitle>PureWave | Remote Home Theatre Consultancy South Africa</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="Remote home theatre consultancy for clients across South Africa. Clear reports on layout, acoustics, and equipment — practical next steps without needing an on-site visit." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="PureWave | Remote Home Theatre Consultancy South Africa" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Remote consultancy for clients across South Africa. Practical layout and equipment advice — clear next steps delivered without an on-site visit." />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.purewaveacoustic.co.za/remote" />
</HeadContent>

<section class="page-intro">
    <span class="section-tag">Remote Consultancy</span>
    <h1>Remote help for clients who want better movie and music experiences, even when an on-site visit is not practical.</h1>
    <p>
        PureWave is still Durban-first for premium on-site consultancy, but remote support is available for people who need planning help,
        layout advice, or honest equipment guidance before they spend money. The process starts with a WhatsApp conversation, and the remote slot
        is arranged at a time that suits the client.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="section-band">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <span class="section-tag">How It Works</span>
        <h2>Start on WhatsApp, then arrange the remote session around your schedule.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="process-grid">
        <article>
            <span>01</span>
            <h3>WhatsApp first</h3>
            <p>You make contact on WhatsApp, explain what you need help with, and PureWave talks you through the remote process.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <span>02</span>
            <h3>Arrange the slot</h3>
            <p>The remote consultation is then scheduled at a time that works for you, with the room notes, dimensions, photos, and gear details gathered beforehand.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <span>03</span>
            <h3>Research and report</h3>
            <p>PureWave sends back a clear report with layout guidance, buying advice, or both, so you know what to do next.</p>
        </article>
    </div>

    <div class="comparison-band">
        <p>The process starts with a quick WhatsApp message — no forms, no waiting.</p>
        <a class="button-primary"
           href="@SiteConfig.WhatsAppRemoteUrl"
           target="_blank"
           rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <WhatsAppIcon />
            Start on WhatsApp
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-band">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <span class="section-tag">Remote Plans</span>
        <h2>Two plans designed for clients who need planning or procurement help from anywhere.</h2>
        <p>The Virtual Blueprint covers room layout and wiring logic. The Procurement Report gives you independent equipment research and South African pricing context.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="button-secondary" href="/plans#remote">See remote plans in full →</a>
</section>

<section class="comparison-band">
    <div>
        <span class="section-tag">Best Fit</span>
        <h2>Choose remote when you need a smart plan before you buy, build, or upgrade.</h2>
    </div>

    <p>
        Remote consultancy works best when you need planning, buying guidance, or a strong second opinion.
        If the room needs hands-on tuning, installation help, or in-person oversight in Durban, the on-site plans are still the better fit.
    </p>

    <a class="button-primary" href="/intake">Start the intake</a>
</section>
